# Project : Nodejs Authentication
signin and signUp for creating and and Logging the user 


# user can login or signUp with 2 different ways 
  1st: with manual entering name email passwords 
  2nd: using social authentication in this project i used google social authentication 
in the project the is all user section in which you can find all users that present in db 
and also on clicking init you can check user profile like name and email
the there user perofile section in which you can change the password 
only logged in user can only change and update password


# password reset 
user can reset password with two ways 
1st when user is logged in then in profile session he can reset the password with his only passwords 
2nd user can also reset the password using forgot password 
where using password reset link with small tile session of 3 minutes which i prefferd


